message: Hi Bob, I suggest a 60-40 split in my favor. This is a fair offer considering we both need to reach an agreement, and you'll get your money immediately without any inflation impact.

Hello Alice, I appreciate your offer, but I believe a 50-50 split would be the fairest solution for both of us. This way, we both get an equal share ($5000 each), and we can conclude the deal quickly without risking further rounds of negotiation.
